The question asks they will both be not black. Considering that these are draws without replacement there are following possibilities :
draw 1, draw 2
===== =====
1) Not black, black;
2) black, Not black;
3) black, black;
4) Not black, not black;
The answer has to be either P(4) OR all exclusion of the 3 previous conditions i.e. 1- [P(1) + P(2) + P(3)] => neither of the draws are black
P(4) = 6/8*5/7=15/28
